body:

The 2023 edition of PyCon DE & PyData Berlin took place 17–19 April 2023 at the bcc Berlin Congress Center. Browse the [archived talks](talks/) and [speakers](speakers/) below, or revisit the [original conference site](https://2023.pycon.de/).
